results.name: Triangle read by rows in which each row is the inverse binomial transform of a diagonal of A089246.
example: The fifth antidiagonal is ( 14 36 32 11 1) which generates 14 50 118 229 395 629 ... by way of the binomial transform.
The fifth row is 14,36,32,11,1. Its binomial transform is 14,50,118,229,395,629... which is a diagonal of A089246.
